fields.name: Effect:
fields.value:
Put 2 players into a Duel with each other. Both players try to get as many card points as possible. Winner gets to gain a card of their choice (including Duel-wons), while the Loser takes 2 HP of damage. 

*Check <#1191646674897084466> for information on Dueling and Card Points. You may not play a Duel?! during rollover.*
